# Flutter Frontend Architecture (CoFit)

> **🎯 Single Source of Truth (SSOT)**
>
> This document is the source of truth for Flutter frontend architecture. If any other rule / doc file conflicts with this one, this one wins.
>
> Not every detail is covered here — when in doubt, raise it in the team and align.

---

## 1. Decision tree: where does my code go?

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start(["What am I writing?"]) --> Q1{"Renders UI?"}
    Q1 -->|Yes| Q2{"Reads providers<br/>via ref.watch?"}
    Q1 -->|No| Q3{"Reads/writes<br/>external data?<br/>(backend / local DB /<br/>cache / file)"}

    Q2 -->|Yes| V["presentation/view/"]
    Q2 -->|No| W["presentation/widget/"]

    Q3 -->|Yes| Q4{"Interface or<br/>implementation?"}
    Q3 -->|No| Q5{"Riverpod<br/>provider declaration?"}

    Q4 -->|Interface| DR["domain/repository/"]
    Q4 -->|Implementation| Q4b{"≥3 cohesive API ops,<br/>or remote + local mix,<br/>or shared client config?"}

    Q4b -->|No| IR["infrastructure/repository/<br/>(inline API calls)"]
    Q4b -->|Yes| DS["infrastructure/datasource/"]

    Q5 -->|Yes| P["provider/"]
    Q5 -->|No| Q6{"App-specific action<br/>or flow?<br/>(this app's way of<br/>achieving a goal)"}

    Q6 -->|Yes| U["usecase/"]
    Q6 -->|No| Q7{"Data shape +<br/>invariants / derived rules?<br/>(would exist without<br/>software)"}

    Q7 -->|Yes| E["domain/entity/"]
    Q7 -->|No| OTHER["share/utils/<br/>or reconsider"]
```

> **Q4b — when to extract a datasource**: Pull raw API calls into `infrastructure/datasource/` if any of the three criteria hold; otherwise keep them inline in the repository impl. 
>
> **Q6 vs Q7**: `usecase` is a verb — *this app's* specific way of achieving a goal (steps, ordering, side-effects; would change if rewritten on a different platform). `entity` is a noun — data + invariants / derived rules that would still exist if there were no software (per Uncle Bob's Clean Architecture). 


### Quick lookup

| What I'm writing | Goes in | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Pure UI component, doesn't read providers | `presentation/widget/` | `bet_card.dart` |
| Page widget, reads providers | `presentation/view/` | `bet_page_view.dart` |
| Riverpod provider declaration | `provider/` | `bet_repository_provider.dart` |
| Data + business rules (Freezed) | `domain/entity/` | `bet_entity.dart` |
| Repository interface (contract) | `domain/repository/` | `bet_repository.dart` |
| Repository implementation | `infrastructure/repository/` | `bet_repository_impl.dart` |
| Raw gRPC / Firebase call | `infrastructure/datasource/` | `bet_service.dart` |
| Multi-repo orchestration action | `usecase/` | `place_bet_usecase.dart` |

