## 3. Data Flow (end-to-end)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant View as View<br/>(HookConsumerWidget)
    participant Provider as Provider<br/>(@riverpod)
    participant UseCase
    participant Domain
    participant Infra as Infrastructure<br/>(Repository impl)
    participant API as Backend<br/>(gRPC/REST/Firebase)

    User->>View: tap / input
    View->>Provider: ref.read(...).method()
    Note over Provider,UseCase: UseCase is OPTIONAL
    Provider->>UseCase: invoke (when orchestration is needed)
    UseCase->>Domain: validate / apply rules
    UseCase->>Infra: call (via domain interface)
    Infra->>API: HTTP / gRPC / Firebase SDK
    API-->>Infra: response / error
    Infra-->>UseCase: domain entity or DomainError
    UseCase-->>Provider: AsyncValue.data / .error
    Provider-->>View: rebuild via ref.watch
    View-->>User: UI update (or SnackBar on error)
```

